title: Cassel replacing Weeden as Cowboys try to win without Romo
text:
> Texas Cassel replacing Weeden as Cowboys try to win without Romo FILE - In this Oct. 11, 2015, file photo, Dallas Cowboys' Matt Cassel (16) throws before an NFL football game against the New England Patriots in Arlington, Texas. Matt Cassel appears on the verge of being named the starter for the Cowboys after Brandon Weeden went 0-3 filling in for Tony Romo. (AP Photo/Brandon Wade, File) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
